Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣妥當嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.23,0:00:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓陛下獨自前往諾齊亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是陛下的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那不怕死的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從以前就一直沒變過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.92,0:00:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於度西斯的瓦解我至感悲痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.83,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.33,0:00:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是這封書簡有交到您手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.43,0:00:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初或許便能遏止\N度西斯的瓦解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.44,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶著記載了安那托勒對度西斯\N所表達的和平意願的這封書簡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.61,0:00:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有兩架先鋒艇\N決定冒險飛越大風暴區…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.56,0:01:09.96,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.03,0:01:13.09,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.63,0:01:20.94,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.01,0:01:27.84,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.91,0:01:34.11,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.19,0:01:42.29,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.49,0:01:56.74,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.81,0:02:11.21,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.29,0:02:20.69,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.81,0:02:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}蘇菲亞升級\NPromotion Sophia
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是副本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.96,0:02:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正本已經與\N三位勇敢的先鋒艇駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起消失在大風暴區當中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.66,0:02:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用先鋒艇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.93,0:02:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導致目前世界瓦解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基爾特公會的無能與怠惰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若要打破基爾特公會的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.74,0:03:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓國家能夠\N以民意為依歸來運作的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們兩國結成同盟外\N已別無其他辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.98,0:03:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是能結成同盟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又將由誰來擔任盟主呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我來擔任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨候鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們長久以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.07,0:03:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直隨著那些鳥群的嚮導\N對這片土地進行侵略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.28,0:03:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深怕在不久的將來\N度西斯即將為冰雪所封閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.85,0:03:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些鳥能夠為安那托勒的土地\N帶來些許滋潤的雨水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信雨候鳥所行經的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.83,0:04:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終將成為連結度西斯與\N安那托勒兩個國家的和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這封書簡我收下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.97,0:04:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這隻被風雪傷得\N無法自由張開的粗手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您願意和我握個手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.39,0:04:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒和度西斯的婚禮是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就送些花給他們好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.97,0:04:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…雲層下實在好髒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.61,0:04:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到大風暴區當中\N居然有航路存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.95,0:04:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說度西斯在\N侵入安那托勒領空時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.62,0:05:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會選擇氣流比較平穩的地點\N來穿越大風暴區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.76,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是從他們把\N這東西交給您這件事看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便可充分得知\N度西斯也非常渴望和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外還有一樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涅斯特司令已經答應了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會全面協助我們找到EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是EXILE的動力音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定可以成為一個\N傑出的副艦長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右滿舵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.65,0:06:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.18,0:06:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從妳開始進入引擎的修理後\N根本就沒有進展嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.72,0:06:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這部份還是讓我自己來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這關係到\N小傢伙能不能飛得起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最重要的一個部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能親手修好它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下我又能用這架來飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用去艦橋嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.79,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是見鬼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.86,0:07:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的小公主居然會說謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是待會兒拿去加菜囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鴿子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.89,0:07:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是自由的象徵耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰日期已決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為山羊月13日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間0400
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳\N你們度西斯都吃鴿子的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，吃了身體會很暖和哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.91,0:08:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，我害那鴿子逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.41,0:08:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莫藍‧謝蘭度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫多妮雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多妮雅‧薛爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.95,0:08:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當天基爾特公會的年輕人\N在滿17歲的這一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須向總帥宣誓效忠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.52,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特全體人員會因這項\N盛大儀式而集合在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.36,0:08:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此這個宣誓日\N對我們聯合軍而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將會是一個最好的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.30,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這項作戰當中\N先鋒艇部隊的位置十分的重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.27,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各自牢牢記住這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你與我是兩顆流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起變成流星吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.61,0:08:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離進行作戰沒有多少時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.05,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，要是沒有這項\N奪取克勞地亞組件的作戰計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們聯合軍是無法獲得勝利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奪取組件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我們自己的手奪回我們的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這明明是我們的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼卻不屬於我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼他討厭我了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是剛才那段話\N說的不得體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，是不是打擾你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.86,0:09:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，基爾特公會\N到底是個怎樣的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言，迪奧殿下\N和總帥大人便代表了一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是基爾特公會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.27,0:09:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，找到一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是維修長給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我先來替您試毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我試過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉你也吃嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.76,0:10:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.53,0:10:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一股清爽的酸味\N與恰到好處的甜味瀰漫口中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的時候\N就要做出好吃的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表情…是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你好吃的表情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.83,0:10:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍他說要離開銀之戰艦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.18,0:10:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼說或許會有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.28,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我其實還滿喜歡銀之戰艦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.52,0:11:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我喜歡的…\N是從銀之戰艦上看見的天空吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.32,0:11:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你裝什麼詩人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.99,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了保護艾兒\N才登上銀之戰艦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然給拉薇添了不少麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但無論是對基爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是對銀之戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都想保護她不受他們傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直誤會了銀之戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.58,0:11:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船確實是\N世界上最安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.28,0:11:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞，塔琪安娜\N還有維修科的大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.62,0:11:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是銀之戰艦在保護著艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.49,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我想通這點\N就同時看清了一件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦的船員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.76,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都是飛翔在\N自己所選擇的天空上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.80,0:11:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說\N我是不會離開銀之戰艦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可別死哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以對生還章發誓\N我是不會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.98,0:12:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼還帶著那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是很有紀念價值的\N第20枚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.02,0:12:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…我是槍兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼祝我們改日再相逢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當班人員各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是艦橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輪機室啟動準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動組件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過熱蒸汽開始注入汽缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,齒輪傳動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.24,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渦輪轉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞地亞開始加壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓力30%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力輸出上昇中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組件，啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組件啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦尾離岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦尾離岸完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦首離岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.67,0:13:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩舷以最微速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩舷最微速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舵轉中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.78,0:13:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦首離岸完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信號確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發自渥卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你幸運\N你賒的酒錢記得要付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒錢記在皇帝的帳上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航路安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.51,0:14:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會離開銀之戰艦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.23,0:15:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.59,0:15:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要以先鋒艇駕駛員的身分\N留在這艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.63,0:15:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新皇帝的加冕儀式要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你駕先鋒艇去做前導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.11,0:15:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我去恭賀蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.51,0:17:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於此，新一代的皇帝陛下\N開啟了新的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒與度西斯\N也將簽下同盟之約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，是蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.73,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看起來好像變了一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.04,0:18:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼式迴轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.53,0:18:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會這一招嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手，太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.23,0:18:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要慶祝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就來一點花俏的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下，冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了，來了，戴芬妮來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.72,0:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃，快逃，快逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，請往這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.14,0:19:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是宣戰布告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，我們上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，變得多漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.87,0:20:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總帥大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認到迪奧殿下\N和魯修拉的行蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.74,0:20:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一架行動異常的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，迪奧是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跑到哪兒寄生去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.56,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加冕儀式會場上\N出現了基爾特戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方在到處灑落薔薇花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輪機室，開到最大航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員進入戰鬥狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭…瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它擊沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下方有副艦長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.19,0:21:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.33,0:21:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個總帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您應該不是那種\N會株連同伴的人才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標，基爾特艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈種穿甲彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砲擊手，命令撤回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.04,0:21:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長現在不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以聽他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坎貝爾，你這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您無論如何忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遲早一定會有攻擊的機會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.18,0:22:40.41,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.12,0:22:47.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.09,0:22:52.39,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.46,0:22:58.09,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.17,0:23:03.87,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.94,0:23:12.61,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.68,0:23:18.59,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.65,0:23:24.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.39,0:23:30.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.20,0:23:35.97,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.04,0:23:46.81,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.45,0:23:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回預告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.92,0:23:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，我把皇帝旗降下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.89,0:23:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還挺機靈的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，隨時要懂得預測未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.10,0:24:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身處劣勢時\N要將艦艇損害減到最小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.57,0:24:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身處優勢時\N就要在敵人的小傷口上抹鹽巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.34,0:24:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.27,0:24:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第19話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.88,0:24:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西西里式防禦\NSicilian Defence
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.21,0:24:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.55,0:24:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟我交換副官啊
